Korede Bello After a long while, the Nigerian musician and songwriter, Korede Bello has taken to his timeline on Twitter to announce the date he is releasing his new single. Many people had previously believed Korede’s music career has come to an end after the hiphop artist has failed to release a new song for a very long time. He wrote: “New Music out next week! Thank you for all the love & patience ❤️”. Korede Bello signed a record deal with Mavin Records in 2014. Korede is best known for his hit singer “God win”. Korede Bello thanks fans for their understanding, love and patience. The question is, will this anticipated new single sparkle Korede’s music career this year 2020? Source